{"type": "article", "id": 8863, "title": "LV 手提箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-24T07:27:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235213Z39Yk6vlphALbnqR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tLouis Vuitton 创意总监 Nicolas Ghesquière 在 2015 年女性秋季发布会上展示了他为 Louis Vuitton 设计的新手提箱。设计灵感来源广泛，从摄影箱到 LV 传统的 “Unpickable” 锁，LV 为我们带来了全新的花纹和款式，材料上选用了 Malletage 金属和有机玻璃袋的结合，可谓颠覆传统之作。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235209gjQRT1W8enSoE2Lm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235210VWna5JSjCx3Elobr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235210rAEXwQlCyLjH7JvF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352117SpDPxuv1Mteijzo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87408313\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235211YNSK34BbhJX0WnDA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352123jwfPHCXriQLm1s0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}